WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:06.000
R is one unit of planned risk. A -1R loss is the planned stop.

00:06.000 --> 00:13.000
Before entry, know the entry, stop, target, and the exact reason for the trade.

00:13.000 --> 00:20.000
The journal is your evidence: screenshots, marker state, decision, result, and lesson learned.
